								<Name>WorkspaceLimitPreset</Name>
								<Comment TxtId=""><![CDATA[Specifies the area in which the endeffector is allowed to move in world coordinates [xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax, zmin, zmax]. Refer to ACINwiki for additional information.]]></Comment>
